=== 开发者支持 ===
{{Main article|Actions on Google}}
2016年12月，Google设立了“[[Actions_on_Google|Actions on Google]]”，一个为Google助理打造的开发者平台。“Actions on Google”允许第三方开发者为Google助理开发内部小程序。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Google Assistant will open up to developers in December with 'Actions on Google' |url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/10/4/13164882/google-assistant-actions-on-google-developer-sdk |accessdate=2017-05-08 |date=2016-10-04 |last=Miller |first=Paul |publisher=[[声音传媒|Vox Media]] |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |archive-date=2020-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516015739/https://www.theverge.com/2016/10/4/13164882/google-assistant-actions-on-google-developer-sdk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Google opens up its Assistant actions to developers |url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/12/08/google-opens-up-its-assistant-actions-to-developers/ |accessdate=2017-05-08 |date=2016-12-08 |last=Low |first=Cherlynn |publisher=[[美国在线|AOL]] |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210132906/https://www.engadget.com/2016/12/08/google-opens-up-its-assistant-actions-to-developers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年3月，Google添加了用于在“Actions on Google”上进行开发的新工具，以支持为Google助理开发游戏。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Game developers rejoice—new tools for developing on Actions on Google |url=https://developers.googleblog.com/2017/03/game-developers-rejoicenew-tools-for.html |accessdate=2017-05-08 |date=2017-03-30 |last=Vemuri |first=Sunil |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |website=Google Developers Blog |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110040336/https://developers.googleblog.com/2017/03/game-developers-rejoicenew-tools-for.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>最初“Actions on Google”只适用于智能音箱Google Home。但2017年5月，“Actions on Google”拓展到了Android和iOS平台，<ref>{{Cite web |title=Third-party actions will soon work on Google Assistant on the phone |url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/17/15648538/google-actions-android-ios-phones-third-party-app-assistant-io-2017 |accessdate=20