== 交互 ==
=== 输入与输出 ===
Google助理支持多种语言的[[语音识别|语音识别]]。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Create shortcut commands |url=https://support.google.com/assistant/answer/7390802?co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid&hl=en |access-date=2018-10-12 |website=supports.google.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012092650/https://support.google.com/assistant/answer/7390802?co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid&hl=en |archive-date=2018-10-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=How To Set Up Google Assistant's Little-Known And Super-Useful Shortcuts |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/kevinmurnane/2017/05/23/how-to-set-up-google-assistants-little-known-and-super-useful-shortcuts/ |date=2017-05-23 |last=Murnane |first=Kevin |dead-url=no |website=Forbes |archive-url=https://archive.today/20181012092147/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kevinmurnane/2017/05/23/how-to-set-up-google-assistants-little-known-and-super-useful-shortcuts/%2314545f6e5e32 |archive-date=2018-10-12 |access-date=2018-12-20 }}</ref>2018年8月，Google助理加入了双语功能，但仅限设备支持的语言使用。<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Google Assistant is now bilingual |url=https://techcrunch.com/2018/08/30/the-google-assistant-is-now-bilingual/ |date=2018-08-30 |last=Lardinois |first=Frederic |website=TechCrunch |access-date=2018-12-20 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110033722/https://techcrunch.com/2018/08/30/the-google-assistant-is-now-bilingual/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[默认选项|默认选项]]下，Google助理不支持文本转录的[[句讀|句讀]]和[[拼寫|拼寫]]等基本功能。不过在Beta版中，英语使用者可以要求“检测并在转录结果中插入标点符号”。语音转文本可以识别逗号、问号和句号。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Getting Punctuation on Speech-to-Text |url=https://cloud.google.com/speech-to-text/docs/automatic-punctuation |website=supports.google.com |access-date=2018-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624205129/https://cloud.google.com/speech-to-text/docs/automatic-punctuation |archive-date=2018-06-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年5月，Google宣布个人助理将支持键盘输入功能。<ref>{{Cite web |title=You can finally use the keyboard to ask Google Assistant questions |url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/17/15648472/google-assistant-keyboard-input-announced-io-2017 |accessdate=2017-05-30 |date=2017-05-17 |last=Bohn |first=Dieter |publisher=[[声音传媒|Vox Media]] |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110033733/https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/17/15648472/google-assistant-keyboard-input-announced-io-2017 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Google Assistant now accepts typed and verbal cues |url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/17/google-assistant-now-accepts-typed-and-verbal-cues/ |accessdate=2017-05-30 |date=2017-05-17 |last=LeFebvre |first=Rob |publisher=[[美国在线|AOL]] |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210135334/https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/17/google-assistant-now-accepts-typed-and-verbal-cues/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>通过键盘输入，用户可以查询与个人助理的历史对话记录，以编辑或删除以前输入的语句。但删除语句时，个人助理会提醒用户它使用以前的活动记录来提供更实用的服务。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Google Assistant on Android now has query history that you can edit or delete |url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/05/18/google-assistant-android-now-query-history-can-edit-delete/ |accessdate=2017-05-30 |date=2017-05-18 |last=Whitwam |first=Ryan |website=Android Police |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110033729/https://www.androidpolice.com/2017/05/18/google-assistant-android-now-query-history-can-edit-delete/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 功能 ===
Google助理可以提供与[[Google即时|Google即时]]类似的功能有搜尋網路、安排行程與鬧鈴、調整用戶裝置的硬體設定，以及顯示用戶Google帳號內的資訊。但不像Google即時資訊，Google助理使用Google的[[自然语言处理|自然语言处理]]介入雙向對話，搜尋結果會以卡片格式呈現並與用戶互動。<ref>{{Cite web |title=The difference between Google Now and Google Assistant |url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/the-difference-between-google-now-and-google-assistant/ |accessdate=2017-03-17 |date=2016-10-04 |last=Purewal |first=Sarah Jacobsson |publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |website=[[CNET|CNET]] |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110033646/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/the-difference-between-google-now-and-google-assistant/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年2月，Google宣布讓Google Home的用戶可以完全以聲音通过{{tsl|en|Google Express||Google Express}}购物服务购买[[全食超市|全食超市]]、[[好市多|好市多]]、[[沃爾格林|沃爾格林]]、{{tsl|en|PetSmart||PetSmart}}和[[Bed_Bath_&_Beyond|Bed Bath & Beyond]]的部分商品。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Google Assistant now helps with your shopping on Google Home (updated) |url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/02/16/google-home-shopping-with-google-assistant/ |accessdate=2017-12-10 |date=2017-02-16 |last=Steele |first=Billy |publisher=[[威訊媒體|Oath Inc.]] |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archive-date=2019-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203010401/https://www.engadget.com/2017/02/16/google-home-shopping-with-google-assistant/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Google Home now lets you shop for everyday items with your voice |url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/google-home-now-lets-you-shop-for-everyday-items-with-your-voice/ |accessdate=2017-12-10 |date=2017-02-16 |last=Martin |first=Taylor |publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |website=[[CNET|CNET]] |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110033756/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/google-home-now-lets-you-shop-for-everyday-items-with-your-voice/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在接下来的几个月中，随着新的合作伙伴关系的建立，其他一些零售商的商品购买也加入了服务。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Order from Walmart by chatting with Google Home |url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/09/